<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .message { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #555; }
    .warning { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .warning strong { color: #856404; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4); }
    .button:hover { background: #c82333; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
    .unsubscribe { font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
    .unsubscribe a { color: #dc3545; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê Password Reset</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="message">Hi there,</p>

      <p>You requested a password reset for your Mediaverse account. Click the button below to set a new password.</p>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This link will expire in 1 hour for your security. If you didn't request this reset, please ignore this email.
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      </div>

      <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="word-break: break-all; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace;">{{actionUrl}}</p>

      {{#if trackingPixel}}{{{trackingPixel}}}{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        ¬© {{year}} Mediaverse. All rights reserved.<br>
        <a href="{{preferencesUrl}}">Manage Account Settings</a>
      </p>
      <p class="unsubscribe">
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe from security emails</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
